s, Cookies, Reptar Coins and more!<br></li><li>Play solo or in co-op, where babies need to stick together to win.<br></li><li>Toggle between nostalgic 8-bit or beautiful HD graphics.<br></li><li>Use your trusty screwdriver to enter engaging boss fights with familiar faces.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2633950/extras/37526a3d05b8ecb429831c334a53dd6e.poster.avif?t=1732122113\" width=512 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2633950/extras/37526a3d05b8ecb429831c334a53dd6e.webm?t=1732122113\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2633950/extras/37526a3d05b8ecb429831c334a53dd6e.mp4?t=1732122113\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
